values:
i think about MT sometimes. i miss the simplicity that was my life. waking up early, eating breakfast with the people i love, having responsibilities and people to look out for, working hard, spending time on the cliff, reading, praying, singing, laughing with bree. i miss it so much. i was so happy and so free and i felt so.... in the right place. i was where i was supposed to be.&nbsp; 
i miss bree. i miss marty and gillian and the ranch. i miss the mountains and campfires and people who love each other.&nbsp; i miss laughing about things that are pure. i miss laughing with other people til i cry. i miss being happy with nothing. 

and i miss tp.
